node.text:
Mental illness, depression, and anxiety look different on everyone. Check on your people's regards of how “put together” they may seem. Remember that even if people don’t seem to be in distress on the outside, believe them, if they say they are.
Repost via @regen_health
📷 Credits punkmom_ on twitter
